name: Shopping-cart

body:
### Welcome to my Shopping Cart Example.
This is a final project done for my Dynamic Web Development class for spring 2016. [This is example is also hosted on Heroku](https://dry-mesa-76339.herokuapp.com/), You may need to wait till the server wakes up.


### Authors and Contributors
This was created by Randy Grullon (@drzgamer), using the [paperclip gem](https://github.com/thoughtbot/paperclip).
